cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the use of neural network classifiers in various tasks such as natural language processing and computer vision, indicating a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper specifically addresses the issue of adversarial examples, which are a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed modifications to the adversarial training method involve reducing computational power, which suggests a focus on neural networks (cs.NE).
